{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/MeshNetworkManager"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/MeshNetworkManager\/localElements","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"extendedModule":"NordicMesh","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh0B14NetworkManagerC13localElementsSayAA7ElementCGvp","title":"localElements","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"localElements","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"text":"Element","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10NordicMesh7ElementC"},{"text":"]","kind":"text"}],"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"An array of Elements of the local Node.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"localElements","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"text":"Element","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:10NordicMesh7ElementC","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"] { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LocalNode"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this property if you want to extend the capabilities of the local"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Node with additional Elements and Models. For example, you may add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"additional Element with Generic On\/Off Client Model if you support this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature in your app. Make sure there is enough addresses for all the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Elements created. If a collision is found, the colliding Elements will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The mandatory Models (Configuration Server and Client and Health Server"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and Client) will be added automatically to the Primary Element,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and should not be added explicitly."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The mesh network must be created or loaded before setting this field,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"otherwise it has no effect.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Important","style":"important","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property has to be set even if no custom Models are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"defined as the set operation initializes the mandatory Models."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It can be set to an empty array."}]}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LocalNode"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Local-Elements","title":"Local Elements"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/meshnetworkmanager\/localelements"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMes